NAME: Config
SHORT: Basic utility cogs such as list the servers the bot is in, usercount, and listing the users with the same discriminator
DESCRIPTION: [p]notify sends a message to every channel the bot is in, [p]channelset sets the channel the bot sends the notification in (you have to use channelset on the server), rest is self explanatory
